{"tid":2337800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"樓上隻狗好嘈可以點","createTime":"2020-12-23T14:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T05:08:57.000Z","uid":211973,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"56ce9d7e9335b2c9c2268cde498bae89b7924380","tid":2337800,"uid":211973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:19:38.000Z","msg":"我係住私樓嘅 屋契係唔比養狗<br />\n<br />\n我樓上佢地今年年頭搬嚟 一開次都聽到小小狗吠聲 不過係好細聲都好間唔中都算， 依家到年尾 可能隻狗大隻左，佢係上面跑嘅話我天花板會有咔咔咔咔聲。同埋佢好定時定候吠。朝早10點會吠10幾分鐘 夜晚6-7會係咁跑同吠。去到9點係最誇張，可能食完飯 會係咁跑嚟跑去 跑成粒鐘都試過。<br />\n因為佢吠唔只影響到我 所以其實有其他鄰居投訴過 好似都吹佢唔漲。我嗰家就同管理處講過都係咁話會跟進，唉屌 又係乜春progress都冇。 <br />\n我老豆斯文人，連我話自己上去㩒佢鐘都唔準。佢驚人地係野蠻人 亂嚟就麻煩。 <br />\n我未知上面係租定買 如果租都可以同業主講返  <br />\n買嘅話係咪冇野做到 <br />\n就算佢違犯屋契都係？"},{"pid":"d72c3e3951372da36095ddea361e050b0aed0f56","tid":2337800,"uid":226466,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"叫佢辭職？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbea773cd3c777216746e4a3a2d17d463184c6d3","tid":2337800,"uid":211973,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d72c3e3951372da36095ddea361e050b0aed0f56","tid":2337800,"uid":226466,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"叫佢辭職？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:24:36.000Z","msg":"真。狗 唔係拎警棍嗰啲"},{"pid":"7212919f66d81e87be0a05eb80abcb5d7ff481f9","tid":2337800,"uid":59669,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:24:54.000Z","msg":"試吓扮狗同樓上隻狗鬥吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003431d6182c074b0eeffd7907bad3a3e9427ab3","tid":2337800,"uid":69650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"電郵去管理公司"},{"pid":"f714bf92d57d8fc5938e3330f0d316ac3f76f620","tid":2337800,"uid":211973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7212919f66d81e87be0a05eb80abcb5d7ff481f9","tid":2337800,"uid":59669,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:24:54.000Z","msg":"試吓扮狗同樓上隻狗鬥吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"有排趕assignment 個人燥燥地 佢一嘈我係窗邊鬧上去  <br />\n屌 但佢係啲自私撚嚟啦應該 <br />\n隻狗嘈到咁 仲好似冇事咁 呢啲言語攻擊真係0 damage"},{"pid":"8090dadfb4584e3a25322cfa92be0a5eaf2e15a6","tid":2337800,"uid":211973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"003431d6182c074b0eeffd7907bad3a3e9427ab3","tid":2337800,"uid":69650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:26:22.000Z","msg":"電郵去管理公司"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:27:32.000Z","msg":"佢地話會跟進 <br />\n屌 搞左個幾月都係冇料到"},{"pid":"a0a20ca0a29bc73770de37ca0a3269fc784b80d9","tid":2337800,"uid":265499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:27:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aa8db2e5c0d50687b2d8232bcb3e704f55ee1f2","tid":2337800,"uid":211973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"係咪可以釘佢契？ 令佢賣唔到樓？"},{"pid":"2f5cc0e981c8f4c10cd3f4227b84845e82fa3d24","tid":2337800,"uid":99032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"燒自己屋企 燒到上面個層 燒埋佢隻狗 完"},{"pid":"664a1f619c61e70cb16873ea9e35349ee78e00a4","tid":2337800,"uid":211973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f5cc0e981c8f4c10cd3f4227b84845e82fa3d24","tid":2337800,"uid":99032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"燒自己屋企 燒到上面個層 燒埋佢隻狗 完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:35:04.000Z","msg":"咁樣好似比佢贏左咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf2954970f3cebc5ab07f4a8c85368d2d3f280c","tid":2337800,"uid":292362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:53:50.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"d494f8a2ec6f2f1f9e959940e618edbb85e85a97","tid":2337800,"uid":347528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56ce9d